      Pattern A (simple scalar):
        SELECT ?obs ?result ?time FROM <http://localhost:8080/graph/observations>
        WHERE { ?obs a sosa:Observation ; sosa:hasSimpleResult ?result ; sosa:resultTime ?time }

      Pattern B (SIO measurement chain):
        PREFIX sio: <http://semanticscience.org/resource/>
        SELECT ?obs ?value ?time FROM <http://localhost:8080/graph/observations>
        WHERE { ?obs a sosa:Observation ; sosa:resultTime ?time ;
                     sio:has-attribute ?mv . ?mv sio:has-value ?value . }

      If Pattern A returns empty, try Pattern B.

